2010-06-10  Marcus Brinkmann  <marcus@g10code.de>

	* gpgme-tool.c (gpgme_server): Use special hack for Windows CE to
	get at stdin and stdout.

	* engine-gpgsm.c (gpgsm_new): Translate returned achild_fds back
	to child_fds.

